#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.merkuro.calendar.metainfo.xml:10
msgid "Merkuro Calendar"
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.merkuro.calendar.metainfo.xml:11
msgid "Manage your tasks and events with speed and ease"
msgstr "Kelola tugas dan acaramu dengan cepat dan mudah"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.merkuro.calendar.metainfo.xml:18
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Kalendar is a calendar application that allows you to manage your tasks "
#| "and events. Kalendar supports both local calendars as well as a multitude "
#| "of online calendars: Nextcloud, Google® Calendar, Outlook®, Caldav, and "
#| "many more."
msgid ""
"Merkuro Calendar is a calendar application that allows you to manage your "
"tasks and events. Kalendar supports both local calendars as well as a "
"multitude of online calendars: Nextcloud, Google® Calendar, Outlook®, "
"Caldav, and many more."
msgstr ""
"Kalendar adalah aplikasi kalender yang memungkinkan kamu mengelola tugas dan "
"acara. Kalendar mendukung baik kalender lokal maupun banyak kalender online: "
"Nextcloud, Google® Calendar, Outlook®, Caldav, dan banyak lagi."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.merkuro.calendar.metainfo.xml:19
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Kalendar gives you many ways to interact with your events. The month view "
#| "provides an overview of the entire month; the week view presents a "
#| "detailed hour-by-hour overview of your week; and the schedule view lists "
#| "all of your upcoming events so that you can easily and quickly plan ahead."
msgid ""
"Merkuro gives you many ways to interact with your events. The month view "
"provides an overview of the entire month; the week view presents a detailed "
"hour-by-hour overview of your week; and the schedule view lists all of your "
"upcoming events so that you can easily and quickly plan ahead."
msgstr ""
"Kalendar memberi kamu banyak cara untuk berinteraksi dengan acaramu. "
"Tampilan bulan memberikan gambaran umum dari seluruh bulan; tampilan pekan "
"menyajikan ikhtisar jam demi jam terperinci dari pekanmu; dan tampilan "
"jadwal mencantumkan semua acara mendatang sehingga kamu bisa dengan mudah "
"dan cepat merencanakan ke depan."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.merkuro.calendar.metainfo.xml:20
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "A tasks view is also available, making it possible for you to manage your "
#| "tasks and subtasks with Kalendar's powerful tree view and its "
#| "customisable filtering capabilities."
msgid ""
"A tasks view is also available, making it possible for you to manage your "
"tasks and subtasks with Merkuro's powerful tree view and its customisable "
"filtering capabilities."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan tugas juga tersedia, memungkinkan kamu untuk mengelola tugas dan "
"subtugasmu dengan tampilan ranting Kalendar yang kuat dan kemampuan "
"pemfilterannya yang dapat disesuaikan."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.merkuro.calendar.metainfo.xml:21
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Kalendar was built with the idea to be usable on desktop, on mobile and "
#| "everything in between."
msgid ""
"Merkuro was built with the idea to be usable on desktop, on mobile and "
"everything in between."
msgstr ""
"Kalendar dibangun dengan ide untuk dapat digunakan di desktop, di ponsel, "
"dan semua yang ada di antaranya."

